sections.heading: to 77-6-10 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1999, ch. 282, § 104 repealed 77-6-1 to 77-6-10 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1941, ch. 150, §§ 1 to 4, 6 to 8, and 10, and as amended by Laws 1945, ch. 96, § 1 and Laws 1977, ch. 247, § 157, relating to dairy industry indemnity, effective July 1, 1999. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1998 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
